Package: spacc
Title: Species Composition Based Prediction Using Neural Networks
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Gilles", "Colling", , email = "gilles.colling@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Predict plot-level attributes from species composition using
    multi-task neural networks. Combines feature hashing for species names
    with learned taxonomic embeddings. Built on a C++ core using libtorch.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
